1.单表select
[select/delete/update…][from…][where…][group by…][having…][order by…]


    SELECT column(s)
    FROM table
    WHERE condition
    ORDER BY col
    GROUP BY col
    HAVING function(col)
2.多表select
    SELECT col(s)
    FROM table1
    JOIN table2
    ON table1.filed1 compopr table2.filed2[AND ON... OR ON...]
    WHERE condition
    ORDER BY col
    GROUP BY col
    HAVING function(col)
    蓝色部分（table2）可以再嵌套JOIN table3
